1/Donald-Trump-and-Kid-Rock-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Donald-Trump-and-Kid-Rock-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Donald-Trump-and-Kid-Rock-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/kid-rock">Kid Rock</a>声称，他和<a href="/artists/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普都</a>因百威淡啤与一名跨性别活动人士的合作关系而与安海斯-布希公司的首席执行官对质。</p><p>这位歌手在肖恩·汉尼提 (Sean Hannity) 的福克斯新闻节目中做客时声称，在 11 月 11 日他与特朗普一起出席 UFC 295 比赛时，两人就安海斯-布希 (Anheuser-Busch) 首席执行官布伦丹·鲍尔·惠特沃斯 (Brendan Ball Whitworth) 就该公司与跨性别活动家和影响者迪伦的合作问题进行了质询。 Mulvaney 是百威淡啤品牌的影响者。</p><p> “所以（特朗普和我）过去了，我们实际上（与惠特沃斯）进行了一次愉快的交谈。我告诉他，‘你向很多像我这样的人发出了信号……通过将那个罐子寄给跨性别孩子，你有点发出信号对我们来说，你们支持这种生活方式，更重要的是，男性参与女子运动或我孙女的更衣室。我们大多数人都在那里划出了一条强硬的路线，”罗克说。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Kid Rock：我从“伸出中指”开始" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7WQ6eHisGT4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续表示，他从未呼吁粉丝“抵制或取消”该品牌。 “我说的是你。你在做什么，把自己融入到这些两极分化的社会问题的对话中？”他问。 “你可以做更多积极的事情，让我们开怀大笑，喝啤酒。”</p><p>今年早些时候，洛克<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-rock-hits-out-at-bud-light-over-parent-companys-partnership-with-trans-activist-3427796">对安海斯布希公司与跨性别活动家和影响者迪伦·马尔瓦尼(Dylan Mulvaney)的合作进行了猛烈抨击</a>，迪伦·穆尔瓦尼是百威淡啤品牌的影响者。</p><p>他发布了一段自己使用半自动步枪向放在河边桌子上的几箱百威淡啤射击的视频。</p><p> “爷爷今天感觉有点兴奋。让我尽可能清楚、简洁地告诉你，”他在喝啤酒之前说道。然后他举起中指喊道：“去他妈的百威淡啤，去他妈的安海斯-布希。”</p><p>他还补充说，他可以与跨性别者和同性恋者“在公共场所共存”。 “做你自己。如果你对我态度冷淡，我也会对你态度冷淡——大多数人就是这样，”他说。 “但是一旦你把我们的孩子带入其中，你就会把仇恨带入其中。让我们那些该死的孩子远离它。这是底线。”</p><p> Recently, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">Dolly Parton</a> defended her decision to keep a duet with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-rock">Kid Rock</a> on the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-defends-kid-rock-collaboration-says-cancel-culture-is-terrible-3539078">tracklist of her new album &#39;Rockstar&#39;, arguing that cancel culture is “terrible”</a> .</p><p> “Somebody was talking to me the other day: &#39;How could you do this [song] with Kid?&#39;” she said in an interview with The <a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/dolly-parton-interview-new-album-rockstar-superbowl-halftime-show-1235634785/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Hollywood Reporter.</em></a> “I said, &#39;Hey, just because I love you don&#39;t mean I don&#39;t love Kid Rock. Just because I love Kid Rock don&#39;t mean I don&#39;t love you.&#39; I don&#39;t condemn or criticise. I just accept and love.”</p><p> She continued: “Like I said, I had done that before, but I&#39;d have probably still done it, because he is a gifted guy, and that song was about a bad boy; it was about a boy that was cheating and mistreating her. But like I say, I love everybody. I don&#39;t criticize, I don&#39;t condone nor condemn. I just accept them. But anyhow, just because I love you don&#39;t mean I don&#39;t love Kid Rock in that God way.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-rock-says-he-and-donald-trump-confronted-ceo-over-bud-light-controversy-at-ufc-fight-3542425">Kid Rock says he and Donald Trump confronted CEO over Bud-Light controversy at UFC fight</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
